          <div class="newcomer-name">
            <a href="https://github.com/elliotllliu/agent-shield" class="tool-link" rel="noopener noreferrer">elliotllliu/agent-shield</a>
          </div>
          <div class="newcomer-meta">TypeScript &middot; 5 stars</div>
          <p>Security scanner for AI agents, MCP servers, and plugins. 30 rules, AST taint tracking, cross-file analysis, and kill chain detection. Billed as a free alternative to Snyk Agent Scan. Security tooling for the AI agent layer is a new category &mdash; watch for more here.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="newcomer">
          <div class="newcomer-name">
            <a href="https://github.com/yoniassia/memclawz" class="tool-link" rel="noopener noreferrer">yoniassia/memclawz</a>
          </div>
          <div class="newcomer-meta">Python &middot; 41 stars</div>
          <p>AI Agent Fleet Memory System combining Qdrant, Mem0, and Neo4j/Graphiti. Composite scoring, compaction engine, temporal knowledge graph, multi-claw federation, and sleep-time reflection &mdash; all exposed as an MCP server. Most complex memory architecture we've indexed to date.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="newcomer">
          <div class="newcomer-name">
            <a href="https://github.com/claude-world/notebooklm-skill" class="tool-link" rel="noopener noreferrer">claude-world/notebooklm-skill</a>
          </div>
          <div class="newcomer-meta">Python &middot; 47 stars</div>
          <p>Bridges NotebookLM's research capabilities into a Claude Code skill + MCP server pipeline: NotebookLM researches, Claude synthesizes and publishes. A workflow-chain pattern that will likely be replicated across other tool pairs.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="newcomer">
          <div class="newcomer-name">
            <a href="https://github.com/MetaBrain-Labs/ComfyUI-MCP-Server-TypeScript" class="tool-link" rel="noopener noreferrer">MetaBrain-Labs/ComfyUI-MCP-Server</a>
